---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Blog | Etacom Technology" description="Insights on software, AI, data, and technology trends in Ethiopia from Etacom Technology.">
  <Header homeLink="/" />

  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
      <div class="container page-hero-content">
        <h1 class="page-hero-title">Blog</h1>
        <p class="page-hero-desc">Insights on technology, innovation, and digital transformation in Ethiopia</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="blog-grid">
          <a href="/blog/hotels-ict-infrastructure" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">ICT Infrastructure</span>
              <span class="blog-date">June 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Why Hotels in Ethiopia Need Modern ICT Infrastructure</h3>
            <p>Guest expectations have changed. Modern hotels need reliable Wi-Fi, IPTV, and smart room controls to stay competitive. Here's what Ethiopian hotels should prioritize.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/blog/ngos-data-analytics" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">AI & Data</span>
              <span class="blog-date">May 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>How NGOs Can Use Data Analytics for Better Decision Making</h3>
            <p>Development organizations collect vast amounts of data but often struggle to turn it into actionable insights. We explore practical approaches to data-driven decisions.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/blog/digital-transformation-sme" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">Digital Transformation</span>
              <span class="blog-date">April 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Digital Transformation for Ethiopian SMEs: Where to Start</h3>
            <p>Going digital doesn't have to be overwhelming. We break down the first steps any Ethiopian business can take to modernize their operations.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/blog/data-center-ethiopian-climate" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">Data Center</span>
              <span class="blog-date">March 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Data Center Design Considerations for the Ethiopian Climate</h3>
            <p>High temperatures and power fluctuations present unique challenges for data center operations in Ethiopia. Here's how to design for reliability.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/blog/custom-software-vs-offtheshelf" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">Software Development</span>
              <span class="blog-date">February 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Custom Software vs Off-the-Shelf: Which Is Right for Your Business?</h3>
            <p>We compare the pros and cons of building custom software versus using ready-made solutions, and help you decide what fits your needs and budget.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a href="/blog/addis-ababa-office" class="blog-card">
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <span class="blog-category">Company News</span>
              <span class="blog-date">January 2026</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Etacom Technology Opens Addis Ababa Office</h3>
            <p>We're expanding! Our new office in Addis Ababa allows us to better serve clients in the capital region and across southern Ethiopia.</p>
            <div class="blog-read-more">
              <span>Read article &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-banner">
      <div class="container cta-content">
        <div>
          <h2>Have a topic suggestion?</h2>
          <p>We'd love to hear what you'd like us to write about.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white">Let Us Know</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 140px 0 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--dark);
  }
  .page-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 500px;
  }
  .blog-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .blog-card {
    display: block;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 28px;
    transition: all var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }
  .blog-card:hover {
    border-color: transparent;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .blog-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .blog-category {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--gray-100);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 50px;
  }
  .blog-date {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  .blog-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .blog-card > p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .blog-read-more {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blog-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
